@HttpFiles_HotAddress = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@IdCaballo = 98126de9-47bf-4b88-8370-c33aa51ca834
### ===============================
### ADMIN
### ===============================

### Login

POST {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/auth/login
Accept: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@admin.com",
    "password": "admin"
}


### Cerrar Session

POST {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/auth/logout
Accept: application/json 


### ver Listado de Caballos Pendientes de Verificación
GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/horses/pending
Accept: application/json

### Ver Detalles de un Caballo 

GET {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/horses/{{IdCaballo}}
Accept: application/json

### Aprobar un Caballo (verified)
### Envía mensaje automático al vendedor vía chat

PUT {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/horses/{{IdCaballo}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "verified"
}

### Rechazar un Caballo (rejected, con motivo)
### Envía mensaje automático al vendedor vía chat con el motivo

PUT {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/horses/{{IdCaballo}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "rejected",
  "reason": "La documentación de propiedad no es válida. Por favor suba un documento actualizado."
}

### Volver a poner en Pendiente

PUT {{HttpFiles_HotAddress}}/admin/horses/{{IdCaballo}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "pending"
}